data.title: Map of salamanca province with municipalities and postal codes
data.meta_description: Map of salamanca, map of the autonomous community of castilla y leon, map of the province of salamanca, roads and highways of salamanca.
data.text:
-Description:

Digital map of the province of Salamanca (Castilla y Le√≥n, Spain) with municipalities, towns and all postal codes.

Two vector files are downloaded: A version in Adobe Illustrator (.ai) which is 100% editable and allows you to modify and customize colors, text and styles, as well as manage (coloring) each municipality and each zip code separately.

Another version in PDF format allows direct printing of the map at the desired size, always with the highest resolution. It also allows the management of layers, which can be displayed and/or hidden to generate various types of customized maps.

The map is optimized for establishing commercial areas, distribution and sales zones, transport routes, graphic design, advertising, etc. Updated to the current year.

-Original measurements:

59x42 cm (A2) (Fully resizable vector file for High-quality printing).
